message.body: Hey, I know we haven't talked in forever, but when do you go back to school? Would u be interested in seeing each other?
I am moving back to school on the 10th but classes don't start til the 14th, so can we plan a date to get together between the 11th and 13th? So excited to see you and catch up!!!!
Yay!!!!!! Have fun in DC! Going there for any reason in particular or just a vacation?
Awwww yay!!!!!!! :) Tell Anna I say hi lol. Hope you two have an awesome trip!
